    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously cared for. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is pristine, showing virtually no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs silently and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a driving experience that feels like it just rolled off the assembly line. Every feature and electronic component works exactly as intended, making this an ideal find for a collector or a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
